akn:section.akn:heading: Application of provisions to Osage County

akn:content.akn:p:
§ 5208. Application of provisions to Osage County This chapter shall not relate to or affect Osage County, Oklahoma. (June 26, 1936, ch. 831, § 8, 49 Stat. 1968.)
Editorial Notes Codification Section was formerly classified to section 508 of this title prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.
